Mark Fischbach Board member


Website
www.redgiantentertainment.com


Red Giant Entertainment, Inc. is a Florida-headquartered comic book publisher and "transmedia" entertainment company first established in 2010. As a transmedia company, Red Giant develops intellectual properties into various ancillary media forms including: movies, television, video games, phone apps, online comics, toy lines, cartoons, T-shirts, and other merchandising opportunities.[1] Red Giant was founded Benny R. Powell, who also served as the head marketing writer for Priceline.com in the company's early days.[2] David Campiti, director and COO, also is CEO of Glass House Graphics. Isen Robbins (CIPO) and Aimee Schoof (CBDO) are both from Intrinsic Value Films and Red Giant Media. Chris Crosby is CTO and the CEO of Keenspot Entertainment.[3] Internet personality Mark "Markiplier" Fischbach joined the board in November 2014.[4]



