			Company Description 


			Red Giant Entertainment, Inc. engages in the development of comic book style properties. Its products are also used in movies, video games, television, novels, toys, apparel, and telephone wireless applications. It operates through the following segments: Advertising, Book Publishing, and Creative. ...
		


                Red Giant Entertainment, Inc. engages in the development of comic book style properties. Its products are also used in movies, video games, television, novels, toys, apparel, and telephone wireless applications. It operates through the following segments: Advertising, Book Publishing, and Creative. The company was founded on January 1, 2011 and is headquartered in Clermont, FL.
            




